messages: An AMD module cannot have multiple name assignments.
JSX element 'any' has no corresponding closing tag.
An element access expression should take an argument.
JSX element 'number' has no corresponding closing tag.
JSX element 'Foo' has no corresponding closing tag.
Unexpected token. A constructor, method, accessor, or property was expected.
Classes can only extend a single class.
An enum member name must be followed by a ',', '=', or '}'.
Identifier expected. 'this' is a reserved word that cannot be used here.
An unary expression with the 'typeof' operator is not allowed in the left-hand side of an exponentiation expression. Consider enclosing the expression in parentheses.
An unary expression with the '-' operator is not allowed in the left-hand side of an exponentiation expression. Consider enclosing the expression in parentheses.
An unary expression with the 'delete' operator is not allowed in the left-hand side of an exponentiation expression. Consider enclosing the expression in parentheses.
An identifier or keyword cannot immediately follow a numeric literal.
JSX element 'IDirectChildrenMap' has no corresponding closing tag.
JSX expressions must have one parent element.
Expected corresponding JSX closing tag for 'span'.
JSX element 'boolean' has no corresponding closing tag.
Identifier expected. 'while' is a reserved word that cannot be used here.
Numeric separators are not allowed here.
Identifier expected. 'void' is a reserved word that cannot be used here.
JSX element 'T' has no corresponding closing tag.
